text: Gabriel Pérez Ramallo (born 29 March 1995) is a Uruguayan footballer who plays as a midfielder for Montevideo Wanderers F.C. in the Uruguayan Primera División. ==References== ==External links== *Profile at Copa Libertadores Website Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Montevideo Wanderers F.C. players Category:Uruguayan Primera División players Category:Uruguayan footballers Category:Association football midfielders
